snippet.title: Best VGM 1008 - Castlevania - Heart of Fire
snippet.description:
See also:
Best VGM 90 - http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=5bTAdrq6leQ
Best VGM 600 - http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=_Ju6JostT7c
Best VGM 1937 - https://youtu.be/Sime7JZrTl0

A collection of my favorite videogame music. Note that most of them are from games I played so I might miss some great ones from games I never played.

NES
Castlevania (1986)
Heart of Fire
Kinuyo Yamashita
